Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本作品是设想在首都东京地区发生巨大地震灾害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在充分调查与查证的基础上所制作的虚构故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原作力求体现真实性 通过模拟实验而著成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也存在与现实事物描写方式不同的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来 只有你一个人真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就可以到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学校等等不是更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.59,0:02:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想试着找一下家人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有悠贵的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.20,0:02:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸妈妈会伤心的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:57.27,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(460,0)}「给 悠 贵」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.09,0:03:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么悠贵会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:03:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵 已经不在了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 悠贵太温柔了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让姐姐伤心 一直都陪在我身边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想和姐姐在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会把你带回家的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 悠贵 到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 也许在家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.33,0:05:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.91,0:06:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 悠贵 不要消失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 我听不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听不到啊 悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐很了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 活着回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 悠贵他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是未来的错 是妈妈不对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单独让你们两个人出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 因为我和你们吵了架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 悠贵他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很感谢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最后都在悠贵身边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是悠贵一直都在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都陪着我到家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让我伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.43,0:08:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让我停止脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让我回到家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我能回来都是因为悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:08:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵一直都在说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家了要和爸爸妈妈说好多话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要和大家一起去台场 还有爷爷家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.39,0:09:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子 想要和大家一起出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要一家人手牵手一起走过大桥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵也不知道说了多少遍 回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.14,0:09:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还没起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.77,0:10:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我画了个青蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 还是不要做了比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早饭做好了 一起来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}东京湾北部地震发生一个月以来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}现在已经逐渐恢复宁静
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}但是现在还有很多区域还没恢复生命线的供给
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}各地制定的对策
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙忙碌碌的 8月马上都要结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.32,0:12:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是日下部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真理小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.09,0:12:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来应该早点来拜访的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.51,0:12:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里的话 我们才是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要麻烦你过来一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子一定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 未来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘦了点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有好好吃饭的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耀眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话活着的人反倒是更辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的一天 太阳升起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围看着都那么美好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.91,0:13:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得会看出神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我丈夫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然从我眼前消失的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葬礼的事完全都不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候是怎么活过来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:14:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 菲娜她啊 每天都在长大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会笑啊 会说话了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打喷嚏的时候会有点像我丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来和悠贵也很像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.61,0:14:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵 一直都在未来的心里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚才给你 不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明已经扔了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵他又捡回来带在身边了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs55}妈妈手机\N\N机器人展怎么样啊\N\N对不起啊没能一起去\N\N我会做好晚饭等你们回来\N\N不要吵架早点回来哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs55}由佳\N\N没事吧\N\N东京 震的好厉害啊\N\N现在我在静冈奶奶家\N\N很担心你 等你联络
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由佳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事呢 由佳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 真理姐姐发的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把手机捡回来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐是手机星人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有手机会寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想有个手机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样就可以和姐姐发好多邮件了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:16:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话不能说话的时候也可以很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有就是也想拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早点回家给妈妈礼物然后再一起拍照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.19,0:16:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我们努力回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵很努力的做了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明头就很痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明身体就不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却没有抱怨一句
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时明明有很多东西都不喜欢吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很硬的面包之类的都好好的吃下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的真的很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:17:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想再见他啊 见悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把未来叫过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和真理小姐分别的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还笑着约定要和她再见面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也需要时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈也不要太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.49,0:17:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.15,0:17:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是要喝点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然晚了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.24,0:17:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是悠贵选的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说妈妈喜欢花的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.59,0:18:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵给妈妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高兴啊 爸爸你看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.93,0:18:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈和未来画的好像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 爸爸的脸是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里充满着悠贵的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是睡着还是醒着还是做着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都会想起悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会一直伤心着难受着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我伤心难过到受不了的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会来找你说说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.39,0:18:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开心的时候高兴得时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会告诉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:19:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的事都告诉给悠贵听
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.61,0:19:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你当了我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.86,0:20:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须一直走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为悠贵在看着
